verbose_text: At the end of stage 3, the islet cell specific marker genes Pdx1, NeuroD, and insulin I were also expressed as in stage 2, whereas the Pax4, Pax6 and MafA genes, the beta-cell functional GK, Kir6.2 and the endocrine insulin II gene were activated (XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG).
